node.text: With the one and ONLY @simonourianmd1 👨‍⚕️! I’ve gotten questions about skin, stretch marks , and just smoothness overall! From being into fitness I’ve seen stretch marks from head to toe! Under arm pits, inner thighs , Glutes , tummy etc! It can be genetic but mainly from your body changing drastically in size, losing weight gaining weight , gaining muscles , growing in size from having babies etc! Thank you @simonourianmd1 for taking care of my skin! I know stretch marks aren’t necessarily a “bad thing” but for those who may want to get rid of them or are a little timid or insecure about hiding them please contact Epion for more details! You won’t regret it! Painless treatments and more!

node.text:
This has easily become my LIFESTYLE. I’m grateful to be able to share my joy for it with you guys!

I started sports in the 7th Grade (basketball, volleyball, track) & played those sports all the way through college. Always played at a very high level , & being active was I knew! I find so much joy and excitement in competition & anything that’s going to challenge me! I may be small, but I can also be UNSTOPPABLE 🦾😈 #qimmahtherapy 

Shot by @nate_zielke_creates

Should I create a program on how I put on more weight & mass?

node.text:
Happy Sunday Funday! 🏖 

FUN FACT : ANother favorite hobby of mine is a game of POOL. I’ve always been super competitive, & I always felt like men shouldn’t be the only ones who kick a** at everything. 🙄 And girls just have to sit on the side and watch cause we’re “incapable “ or not strong enough or blah blah. It’s actually a lot of fun. I figured it’d be a nice switch up and have the Women leave with the 🥇 🎱

Ladies if you want to beat your boyfriend at a game of Pool, I’ll be holding classes soon 🤪🤫😈 just FYI

& YES, I Won 😁
Haha have a beautiful day! And stay Blessed!

GLUTE FLEX ‼️

THICK FIT W/ some Dimples! 🤫🦾Loving the weight I’ve put on, & I love being a little thicker. My physique was so petite and tight growing up, I know as I got older and my body started to change that I had to cater to it differently. While also appreciating Women Hood 😝

Fall in love with all the dimples, stretch marks, and changes ladies! It’s all beautiful because it makes you, YOU!
